<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<!-- B案: データドリブンアプローチ。数字・グラフ・比較表で説得力を出す。ダッシュボード風レイアウト、SVGチャート、進捗バー -->
<script src="../auth.js"></script>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>UcarPAC Store Screenshot Prototypes | ASO 17.3%→25%</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #F84CA2;
      --dark-blue: #1c2663;
      --white: #FFFFFF;
      --text-black: #404040;
      --text-gray: #737373;
      --text-disabled: #B3B3B3;
      --text-placeholder: rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.3);
      --text-light-blue: #bfdbfe;
      --text-under-blue: #0056BA;
      --button-gray: #CACEE2;
      --button-link1: #4099FF;
      --button-link2: #40BFFF;
      --back-white: #FAFAFA;
      --back-gray: #EDF1F4;
      --back-gray2: #e6e6e6;
      --back-blue: #091355;
      --back-dark-blue: #0a1348;
      --back-light-pink: #ffd8e8;
      --back-light-blue: #6fc2ff;
      --error: #EB4646;
      --shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.11);
      --ruled-line: #F2F2F2;
      --border-gray: #7C7C7C;
      --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(90deg, #1ddcff, #4db4ff);
      --gradient-pink: linear-gradient(90deg, #f84ca2, #f84ca2);
      --gradient-dark: linear-gradient(135deg, #091355 0%, #1d2e93 100%);
      --gradient-panel: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.98) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.92) 100%);
      --gradient-surface: linear-gradient(180deg, #eef6ff 0%, #f7fbff 44%, #fff6fb 100%);
      --gradient-mesh:
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.22), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 0%, rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.24), transparent 25%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 82% 78%, rgba(111, 194, 255, 0.22), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #ecf4ff 0%, #f7fbff 48%, #fff6fb 100%);
      --font-sans: "Noto Sans JP", "Hiragino Sans", "Yu Gothic", sans-serif;
      --font-number: "Noto Sans JP", "Hiragino Sans", sans-serif;
      --space-1: 4px;
      --space-2: 8px;
      --space-3: 12px;
      --space-4: 16px;
      --space-5: 20px;
      --space-6: 24px;
      --space-7: 27px;
      --space-8: 32px;
      --space-9: 38px;
      --radius-sm: 5px;
      --radius-md: 12px;
      --radius-card: 13px;
      --radius-lg: 16px;
      --radius-chip: 22px;
      --radius-button: 30px;
      --phone-width: 375px;
      --phone-height: 812px;
      --shadow-light: 0 10px 30px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      --shadow-medium: 0 20px 48px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.14);
      --shadow-heavy: 0 30px 80px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.18);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100%;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
      color: var(--text-black);
      background: var(--gradient-mesh);
    }

    body {
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
    }

    button {
      font: inherit;
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 1360px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px 14px 60px;
    }

    .page::before,
    .page::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      width: 240px;
      height: 240px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      filter: blur(34px);
      opacity: 0.42;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .page::before {
      top: 80px;
      left: -50px;
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.18);
    }

    .page::after {
      right: -60px;
      bottom: 20px;
      background: rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.18);
    }

    .masthead,
    .control-panel,
    .screen-deck,
    .insight-grid,
    .source-board {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .masthead {
      padding: 24px 18px 22px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .masthead::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -40px -48px auto;
      width: 220px;
      height: 220px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.22), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 36px;
      padding: 0 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.08);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .eyebrow .pulse {
      width: 9px;
      height: 9px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--pink);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 8px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
      animation: pulse 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 10px;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);
      line-height: 1.16;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 900;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 820px;
      color: #64708d;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .lead strong {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .kpi-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .kpi-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: var(--gradient-panel);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
    }

    .kpi-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .kpi-value {
      margin-top: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      gap: 8px;
      font-family: var(--font-number);
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .kpi-value span {
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .progress-rail {
      margin-top: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #e8edf8;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .progress-fill {
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--gradient-primary);
      width: var(--fill, 50%);
      transition: width 320ms ease;
    }

    .progress-fill.is-pink {
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
    }

    .control-panel {
      margin-top: 18px;
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .control-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .control-title {
      min-width: 110px;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .chip-group {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .chip {
      appearance: none;
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.1);
      min-height: 43px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-button);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, background 180ms ease, color 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
    }

    .chip:hover,
    .chip.is-active {
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.16);
    }

    .chip.is-accent:hover,
    .chip.is-accent.is-active {
      background: var(--pink);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.22);
    }

    .status-note {
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.94), rgba(29, 46, 147, 0.88));
      color: var(--white);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .status-copy {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    }

    .status-copy strong {
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .status-badges {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .status-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--text-light-blue);
    }

    .screen-deck {
      margin-top: 22px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .screen-card {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      opacity: 1;
      transition: transform 240ms ease, opacity 240ms ease;
    }

    .screen-card.is-hidden {
      display: none;
    }

    .screen-meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 0 2px;
    }

    .screen-label {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      min-height: 34px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .screen-label .index {
      display: inline-grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .screen-platform {
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .screen-caption {
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .phone {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100%, var(--phone-width));
      min-height: var(--phone-height);
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 42px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.82), rgba(255,255,255,0.58)),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #edf3fb, #fff7fc);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-heavy);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .phone::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 10px;
      left: 50%;
      width: 120px;
      height: 30px;
      margin-left: -60px;
      border-radius: 0 0 18px 18px;
      background: #16215e;
      z-index: 4;
    }

    .phone-screen {
      position: relative;
      min-height: calc(var(--phone-height) - 28px);
      padding: 18px 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 30px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7fbff 0%, #eef5ff 48%, #fff5fa 100%);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .phone-screen::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 10%, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.16), transparent 18%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 12% 22%, rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.18), transparent 20%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .status-bar {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .status-icons {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .status-icons span {
      display: block;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      opacity: 0.86;
    }

    .status-icons span:nth-child(1) {
      width: 11px;
    }

    .status-icons span:nth-child(2) {
      width: 18px;
    }

    .status-icons span:nth-child(3) {
      width: 24px;
    }

    .shot-header,
    .shot-body,
    .shot-footer {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .shot-header {
      margin-top: 18px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .stack-badges {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      min-height: 32px;
      padding: 0 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .pill.dark {
      background: rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.92);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .pill.soft {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
    }

    .pill.pink {
      background: var(--pink);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .pill.blue {
      background: rgba(29, 220, 255, 0.16);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .shot-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 30px;
      line-height: 1.22;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .shot-lead {
      margin: 0;
      color: #64708d;
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: var(--gradient-dark);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.18);
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .car-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .car-thumb {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.18), rgba(255,255,255,0.04)),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #3648bf, #0a1348);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    }

    .car-thumb svg {
      width: 44px;
      height: 28px;
    }

    .car-name {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .car-spec {
      margin: 2px 0 0;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.3fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .price-panel {
      display: grid;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .price-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .price-value {
      font-size: 42px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .price-foot {
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .mini-kpi-box {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mini-kpi-box strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.2;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .mini-kpi-box span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .content-card {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 32px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
    }

    .section-heading {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-heading h3 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .section-heading p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .metric-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .metric-box {
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #f4f8ff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .metric-box strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .metric-box span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .axis {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-top: 6px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .primary-button,
    .secondary-button {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 43px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-button);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      font-weight: 900;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 180ms ease, filter 180ms ease, box-shadow 180ms ease;
    }

    .primary-button {
      margin-top: 14px;
      background: var(--gradient-primary);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(64, 153, 255, 0.22);
    }

    .secondary-button {
      margin-top: 10px;
      background: var(--gradient-pink);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.2);
    }

    .primary-button:hover,
    .secondary-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      filter: saturate(1.06);
    }

    .hint-line {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .forecast-badges {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .forecast-badge {
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.08);
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .expense-total {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .expense-value {
      font-size: 40px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .expense-sub {
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .ring-wrap {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .ring {
      position: relative;
      width: 92px;
      height: 92px;
    }

    .ring svg {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      transform: rotate(-90deg);
    }

    .ring-center {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .ring-center strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.1;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .expense-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .expense-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .expense-dot {
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
    }

    .expense-bar {
      position: relative;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #ebf1f8;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .expense-fill {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0 auto 0 0;
      width: var(--width, 40%);
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.9), rgba(77, 180, 255, 0.9));
      transition: width 280ms ease;
    }

    .forecast-switch {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 4px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #eef4ff;
    }

    .forecast-switch button {
      appearance: none;
      min-height: 38px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 180ms ease, color 180ms ease;
    }

    .forecast-switch button.is-active {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--pink);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.08);
    }

    .forecast-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .forecast-box {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: #f6f9ff;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .forecast-box strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .forecast-box span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 2px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .timing-score {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.08), rgba(64, 153, 255, 0.08));
    }

    .timing-score .score-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .timing-score .score-top strong {
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .timing-score .score-top span {
      color: var(--pink);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .timing-score p {
      margin: 8px 0 0;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .compare-hero {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: linear-gradient(140deg, #091355 0%, #14206d 52%, #f84ca2 180%);
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.18);
    }

    .compare-hero strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 54px;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .compare-hero small {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .compare-hero p {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
    }

    .compare-stage {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 4px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .compare-stage button {
      appearance: none;
      min-height: 36px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: transparent;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      font-weight: 900;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 180ms ease, color 180ms ease;
    }

    .compare-stage button.is-active {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .compare-table {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 14px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .compare-table th,
    .compare-table td {
      padding: 10px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e6ecf7;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .compare-table th {
      background: #f2f6ff;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: #59708e;
    }

    .compare-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .compare-table .brand {
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
    }

    .compare-table .ucarpac {
      background: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.07);
    }

    .compare-table .accent {
      color: var(--pink);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .compare-note {
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.06);
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .shot-footer {
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .footer-caption {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .insight-grid {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    }

    .panel h2 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .panel p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hypothesis-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .hypothesis-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(9, 19, 85, 0.05), rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.05));
    }

    .hypothesis-index {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      background: var(--dark-blue);
      color: var(--white);
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .hypothesis-item strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .hypothesis-item span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 3px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .mini-board {
      margin-top: 16px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mini-board .tile {
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: #f4f8ff;
    }

    .mini-board strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.3;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .mini-board span {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 11px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .source-board {
      margin-top: 24px;
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .source-head {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: flex-end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .source-head h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .source-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .source-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .source-card {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(244, 248, 255, 0.92), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9));
      border: 1px solid rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(28, 38, 99, 0.06);
    }

    .source-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--dark-blue);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .source-card p {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: var(--text-gray);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .source-card a {
      color: var(--text-under-blue);
      font-weight: 900;
      text-decoration: none;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .source-card a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .policy-note {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255, 242, 232, 0.9);
      border: 1px solid rgba(240, 198, 173, 0.8);
      color: #9f3c0b;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .shot-svg {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .line-path {
      fill: none;
      stroke: var(--pink);
      stroke-width: 4;
      stroke-linecap: round;
      stroke-linejoin: round;
      stroke-dasharray: 320;
      stroke-dashoffset: 320;
      animation: dash 1.6s ease forwards;
    }

    .area-path {
      fill: rgba(248, 76, 162, 0.12);
    }

    .dot {
      fill: var(--pink);
      stroke: var(--white);
      stroke-width: 3;
      animation: pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .bar-bg {
      fill: #e8eff9;
    }

    .bar-fill {
      fill: url(#expenseGradient);
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1.08);
        opacity: 0.84;
      }
    }

    @keyframes dash {
      to {
        stroke-dashoffset: 0;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1180px) {
      .screen-deck,
      .insight-grid,
      .source-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .kpi-strip {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .page {
        padding: 14px 12px 48px;
      }

      .masthead,
      .control-panel,
      .panel,
      .source-board {
        border-radius: 22px;
      }

      .kpi-strip {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .control-title {
        min-width: auto;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .ring-wrap,
      .forecast-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .phone {
        border-radius: 34px;
      }

      .phone-screen {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .source-grid,
      .mini-board {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .kpi-strip {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .metric-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .shot-title {
        font-size: 28px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="page">
    <section class="masthead">
      <div class="eyebrow"><span class="pulse"></span>Store PV→DL率 改善テーマ / 2026-04-01</div>
      <h1>数字が先に刺さる。<br>UcarPACの強みを3枚で伝えるASOスクショ。</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        B案は<strong>現状CVR 17.3% → KPI 25%</strong>の差分を埋めるためのデータドリブン構成です。
        1枚目で<strong>AI査定の独自価値</strong>、2枚目で<strong>出費管理と売り時判断</strong>、3枚目で<strong>「相場を見るだけなら電話0本」</strong>を比較で理解させます。
        AppleのProduct Page OptimizationとGoogle Playのストア差し替え前提で、見出しと数値の理解速度を優先しています。
      </p>

      <div class="kpi-strip">
        <article class="kpi-card">
          <div class="kpi-label">現在のストアCVR</div>
          <div class="kpi-value" id="currentCvr">17.3<span>%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-rail"><div class="progress-fill" id="currentBar" style="--fill:69.2%;"></div></div>
        </article>
        <article class="kpi-card">
          <div class="kpi-label">目標CVR</div>
          <div class="kpi-value" id="targetCvr">25.0<span>%</span></div>
          <div class="progress-rail"><div class="progress-fill is-pink" id="targetBar" style="--fill:100%;"></div></div>
        </article>
        <article class="kpi-card">
          <div class="kpi-label">必要改善幅</div>
          <div class="kpi-value" id="gapValue">+7.7<span>pt</span></div>
          <div class="progress-rail"><div class="progress-fill" id="gapBar" style="--fill:30.8%;"></div></div>
        </article>
        <article class="kpi-card">
          <div class="kpi-label">検証パターン</div>
          <div class="kpi-value" id="variantValue">3<span>screens</span></div>
          <div class="progress-rail"><div class="progress-fill" style="--fill:84%;"></div></div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="control-panel">
      <div class="control-row">
        <div class="control-title">KPIシナリオ</div>
        <div class="chip-group" id="scenarioControls">
          <button class="chip is-active" data-scenario="baseline">現状 17.3%</button>
          <button class="chip" data-scenario="mid">仮説 21.8%</button>
          <button class="chip is-accent" data-scenario="goal">目標 25.0%</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="control-row">
        <div class="control-title">表示スクリーン</div>
        <div class="chip-group" id="filterControls">
          <button class="chip is-active" data-filter="all">3枚まとめて表示</button>
          <button class="chip" data-filter="a">スクショAのみ</button>
          <button class="chip" data-filter="b">スクショBのみ</button>
          <button class="chip" data-filter="c">スクショCのみ</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="status-note">
        <div class="status-copy" id="statusCopy">
          現状想定では、<strong>独自機能の理解不足</strong>がCVRの目詰まり。まずは「AI査定」「将来予測」「電話0本の入口」を最短で読ませる構成を優先。
        </div>
        <div class="status-badges">
          <span class="status-badge">iOS向けA: AI査定全面</span>
          <span class="status-badge">Android向けB: 出費管理 + 予測</span>
          <span class="status-badge">比較訴求C: 電話0本</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="screen-deck" id="screenDeck">
      <article class="screen-card" data-screen="a">
        <div class="screen-meta">
          <div class="screen-label"><span class="index">A</span>AI査定を全面に出す</div>
          <div class="screen-platform">iOS向け / PPO候補</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phone">
          <div class="phone-screen">
            <div class="status-bar">
              <span>9:41</span>
              <div class="status-icons">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="shot-header">
              <div class="stack-badges">
                <span class="pill dark">AI査定</span>
                <span class="pill soft">個人情報なし</span>
                <span class="pill pink">相場チェック10秒</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="shot-title">AIが今と<br>3か月後を予測</h2>
              <p class="shot-lead">
                「まずは価格だけ知りたい」ユーザー向けに、登録直後の価値を1画面で伝えるスクショ。
                愛車の現在価格と将来予測を同時表示し、AI査定の独自性を先頭で理解させます。
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="shot-body">
              <section class="hero-card">
                <div class="car-row">
                  <div class="car-thumb" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 88 54" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path d="M18 30L28 18H57L70 23L77 30V38H74C73 42 70 45 65 45C60 45 57 42 56 38H32C31 42 28 45 23 45C18 45 15 42 14 38H11V30H18Z" fill="white" opacity="0.92"/>
                      <circle cx="23" cy="39" r="6" fill="#091355"/>
                      <circle cx="65" cy="39" r="6" fill="#091355"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="car-name">トヨタ ハリアー Z Leather Package</p>
                    <p class="car-spec">2021年式 / 32,400km / パール / 2WD</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-grid">
                  <div class="price-panel">
                    <div class="price-label">AI査定の現在価値</div>
                    <div class="price-value">286万円</div>
                    <div class="price-foot">先月比 +4万円 / 3か月後予測 279万円</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="mini-kpi-box">
                    <strong>88</strong>
                    <span>需要スコア<br>春のSUV需要</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>

              <section class="content-card">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <div>
                    <h3>価格推移シミュレーション</h3>
                    <p>現在の相場 + 将来予測を1画面で訴求</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="pill blue">-7万円 / 3か月</span>
                </div>
                <svg class="shot-svg" viewBox="0 0 320 170" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="価格推移グラフ">
                  <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="lineGradientA" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0">
                      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1ddcff" />
                      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f84ca2" />
                    </linearGradient>
                  </defs>
                  <path class="area-path" d="M22 130C56 115 78 88 108 82C142 74 164 86 196 98C226 110 256 116 298 122V150H22V130Z"/>
                  <path d="M22 24V150H300" stroke="#d7e1f0" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <path d="M22 52H300" stroke="#eef3fb" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <path d="M22 86H300" stroke="#eef3fb" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <path d="M22 118H300" stroke="#eef3fb" stroke-width="2"/>
                  <path class="line-path" style="stroke:url(#lineGradientA);" d="M22 130C56 115 78 88 108 82C142 74 164 86 196 98C226 110 256 116 298 122"/>
                  <circle class="dot" cx="108" cy="82" r="6"/>
                  <circle class="dot" cx="196" cy="98" r="6"/>
                  <circle class="dot" cx="298" cy="122" r="6"/>
                  <text x="14" y="27" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">300万円</text>
                  <text x="14" y="151" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">260万円</text>
                  <text x="22" y="164" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">今月</text>
                  <text x="96" y="164" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">1か月後</text>
                  <text x="176" y="164" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">3か月後</text>
                  <text x="266" y="164" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">6か月後</text>
                </svg>
                <div class="metric-grid">
                  <div class="metric-box">
                    <strong>286万円</strong>
                    <span>今の相場</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="metric-box">
                    <strong>279万円</strong>
                    <span>3か月後</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="metric-box">
                    <strong>271万円</strong>
                    <span>6か月後</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="forecast-badges">
                  <span class="forecast-badge">写真を追加すると精度アップ</span>
                  <span class="forecast-badge">査定後にダッシュボードへ保存</span>
                </div>
                <button class="primary-button" type="button">AIで愛車の相場を見る</button>
                <div class="hint-line">相場チェックは個人情報不要。売る時だけ相談へ進む設計。</div>
              </section>
            </div>

            <div class="shot-footer">
              <div class="footer-caption">スクショAの狙い: 「アプリを入れる理由」をAI査定の即時価値で一発理解させる。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="screen-caption">
          大見出しは「AI」「今」「3か月後」の3語に絞り、相場確認アプリとしての独自性を最初の1枚で認知させる設計です。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="screen-card" data-screen="b">
        <div class="screen-meta">
          <div class="screen-label"><span class="index">B</span>出費管理 + 将来予測</div>
          <div class="screen-platform">Android向け / Main Listing候補</div>
        </div>
        <div class="phone">
          <div class="phone-screen">
            <div class="status-bar">
              <span>9:41</span>
              <div class="status-icons">
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
                <span></span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="shot-header">
              <div class="stack-badges">
                <span class="pill dark">出費管理</span>
                <span class="pill soft">将来予測</span>
                <span class="pill blue">Android訴求</span>
              </div>
              <h2 class="shot-title">維持費も売り時も<br>ひと目でわかる</h2>
              <p class="shot-lead">
                「売るか未定でも入れる理由」を作る2枚目。毎月の出費と将来価格を1つのダッシュボードに統合し、
                車を持ち続ける期間でも価値を感じる体験を前面に出します。
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="shot-body">
              <section class="content-card">
                <div class="expense-total">
                  <div>
                    <div class="price-label" style="color:#66748d;">今月の車の出費</div>
                    <div class="expense-value">48,600円</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="expense-sub">
                    年換算 58.3万円<br>
                    先月比 -6,200円
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="ring-wrap">
                  <div class="ring">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 120 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="出費の構成比">
                      <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="46" fill="none" stroke="#e8eef8" stroke-width="14"/>
                      <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="46" fill="none" stroke="#f84ca2" stroke-width="14" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="86 289"/>
                      <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="46" fill="none" stroke="#4db4ff" stroke-width="14" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="70 305" stroke-dashoffset="-92"/>
                      <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="46" fill="none" stroke="#091355" stroke-width="14" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="56 319" stroke-dashoffset="-168"/>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="ring-center"><div><strong>4</strong>カテゴリ</div></div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="expense-list">
                    <div class="expense-item">
                      <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#f84ca2;"></span>
                      <div class="expense-bar"><span class="expense-fill" style="--width:38%;"></span></div>
                      <span>ガソリン 18,400円</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expense-item">
                      <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#4db4ff;"></span>
                      <div class="expense-bar"><span class="expense-fill" style="--width:31%;"></span></div>
                      <span>駐車場 15,000円</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expense-item">
                      <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#091355;"></span>
                      <div class="expense-bar"><span class="expense-fill" style="--width:18%;"></span></div>
                      <span>保険 8,700円</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="expense-item">
                      <span class="expense-dot" style="background:#6fc2ff;"></span>
                      <div class="expense-bar"><span class="expense-fill" style="--width:13%;"></span></div>
                      <span>車検積立 6,500円</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <button class="primary-button" type="button">出費と相場をまとめて管理</button>
              </section>

              <section class="content-card">
                <div class="section-heading">
                  <div>
                    <h3>売り時シミュレーション</h3>
                    <p>3か月後 / 6か月後 を切り替え表示</p>
                  </div>
                  <span class="pill pink" id="forecastDelta">-7万円見込み</span>
                </div>

                <div class="forecast-switch" id="forecastControls">
                  <button class="is-active" type="button" data-range="3m">3か月後</button>
                  <button type="button" data-range="6m">6か月後</button>
                </div>

                <svg class="shot-svg" viewBox="0 0 320 144" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" role="img" aria-label="将来予測グラフ">
                  <defs>
                    <linearGradient id="expenseGradient" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0">
                      <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#1ddcff" />
                      <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#f84ca2" />
                    </linearGradient>
                  </defs>
                  <rect x="22" y="22" width="278" height="92" rx="14" fill="#f8fbff"/>
                  <path d="M40 98C74 86 108 74 140 72C172 70 208 78 244 88C262 92 278 98 290 102" fill="none" stroke="url(#expenseGradient)" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  <circle cx="140" cy="72" r="5" fill="#f84ca2"/>
                  <circle cx="244" cy="88" r="5" fill="#f84ca2"/>
                  <circle cx="290" cy="102" r="5" fill="#f84ca2"/>
                  <text x="36" y="118" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">今</text>
                  <text x="132" y="118" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">3か月</text>
                  <text x="236" y="118" font-size="10" fill="#7a879d" font-weight="700">6か月</text>
                  <text x="252" y="62" font-size="10" fill="#f84ca2" font-weight="800">下落予兆あり</text>
                </svg>

                <div class="forecast-grid">
                  <div class="forecast-box">
                    <strong id="forecastPrice">279万円</strong>
                    <span id="forecastLabel">3か月後の予測価格</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="forecast-box">
                    <strong id="forecastAction">待ちすぎ注意</strong>
                    <span id="forecastActionLabel">売り時アドバイス</span>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="timing-score">
                  <div class="score-top">
                    <strong>売り時指数</strong>
                    <span id="timingScore">78 / 100</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="progress-rail"><div class="progress-fill is-pink" id="timingBar" style="--fill:78%;"></div></div>
                  <p id="timingCopy">
                    SUV需要が強い一方、夏以降は新型流入の影響で下落しやすい想定。今季のうちに価格確認を促すコピーと相性が良い。
                  </p>
                </div>

                <button class="secondary-button" type="button">売るタイミングをチェック</button>
              </section>
            </div>

            <div class="shot-footer">
              <div class="footer-caption">スクショBの狙い: 「今すぐ売らない人」もDLする理由を、出費管理 + 売り時判断で補強する。</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="screen-caption">
          Android向けは説明量を少し増やし、継続利用の理由を先回り。価格変動を見るだけでなく、維持費の可視化を一緒に出してリテンション寄りに寄せています。
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="screen-card" data-screen="c">
        <div class="screen-meta">
